Title: Two-Dimensional Quantum Poincar\'E Group

Authors: Jakub Rembielinski & Waclaw Tybor

Comments: LaTeX (A4 style), 6pp, KFT UL 5/93

Quantum Poincar\'e-Weyl group in two dimensional quantum Minkowski space-timeis considered and an appriopriate relativistic kinematics is investigated. Itis claimed that a consistent approach to the above questions demands a kind ofa ``quantum geometry'' in the $q$-deformed space-time.